It stars [[:ru:%D0%A0%D1%8B%D0%B1%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2, %D0%9D%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B9 %D0%9D%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%87|Nikolay Rybnikov]] and [[Inna Makarova]].
